    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Any of various garments, as loose blouses, jump suits, caftans, or sarongs, worn over a swimsuit, exercise clothing, or the like.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
